     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA08d094n2-ptr" id="PJA08d094n2">2</a>
      <p>An act for the more effectual preventing forestalling and engrossing (Session Laws, 1779, <span class="ref-terms">Ch.</span> XVII, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Laws of Maryland</span>, Annapolis, [1779], <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Charles Evans and others, comps., &lt;i&gt;American Bibliography: A Chronological Dictionary of All Books, Pamphlets and Periodical Publications Printed in the United States of America&lt;/i&gt; [[16391800]], Chicago and Worcester, 19031959; 14 vols. ]">Evans</span>, No. 16333).</p>
